REMOTE_DICTIONARY_SERVER

public static final java.lang.String REMOTE_DICTIONARY_SERVER
The dictionary can run as a remove host. Use RemoteEntityRecogntion in this case. This field holds the server's name.

REMOTE_DICTIONARY_PORT

public static final int REMOTE_DICTIONARY_PORT
The dictionary can run as a remote host. Use RemoteEntityRecogntion in this case. This field holds the server's port. If you use multiple dictionaries (inter-species case), use the file taxonToServerPort.txt.
